locality.
</emphasis>
Albeit not explicitly reported, the geographic coordinates on the label point to Ribeirão Cascalheira (
<collectingRegion id="49A1F80D9417FFCDBAD63FC1FEE9FA4F" box="[222,372,1483,1509]" country="Brazil" name="Mato Grosso" pageId="24" pageNumber="275">Mato Grosso</collectingRegion>
